{"tid":1089900,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"吳卓羲宣佈重返樂壇","createTime":"2019-04-03T06:01:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T02:02:36.000Z","uid":228995,"like":30,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"35949ae3a9c04d30a43fe0f197a79d535ec2e8a7","tid":1089900,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T06:01:49.000Z","msg":"//吳卓羲和鄧智偉出席《博愛醫院百周年（己亥年）董事局就職晚宴》，吳卓羲表示上台獻唱「別怪她」，擔任作曲的鄧智偉負責彈鋼琴，今次兩人合作而頻頻見面，大家計劃今年將「別怪她」製作15周年下集版本。當笑他今年可參加樂壇頒獎禮，跟林峯對撼？他說：「唔係咩呀！講笑，只係15周年，再做返15年前覺得幾有趣。」吳卓羲表示計劃會推出EP，預計有4、5首歌，就算並非鄧智偉作歌也一定擔任監製。在旁的鄧智偉笑指吳卓羲近排好勤力，不過只是近幾日的事。//<br />\n<br />\n2020年我最喜愛男歌手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eb97b64a79bfaff28eaa194bd4a943c7f50cf19","tid":1089900,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":35,"score":-35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T06:05:26.000Z","msg":"祝福聲想你都聽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a637aa2c7c107e248824c49b586fcd33d702e4","tid":1089900,"uid":32403,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T06:06:11.000Z","msg":"花師奶終於有新版本唱"},{"pid":"09afe7afc486fb68150b17c27faa85fbb421fe5b","tid":1089900,"uid":69614,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T06:07:48.000Z","msg":"別怪她多人識都係因為花師奶"},{"pid":"52c54d16f676672637adee1f260178991025efe2","tid":1089900,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T06:10:03.000Z","msg":"做咩遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又唔係乜經典人物, 邊個咁得閒想同佢懷緬15週年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de27caa845092d196b1bec62bb64321d552d2de6","tid":1089900,"uid":84926,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T06:10:20.000Z","msg":"俾柴九搶歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab133620875a8d8afbde750e59f